Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.23,0:00:37.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}依舊波濤洶涌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.53,0:00:44.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說 你吃什麼才會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼...其實也沒吃什麼特別的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:49.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蠢貨...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:54.05,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哎 這麼樣才能變大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:53.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\blur5}不能這麼幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:55.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\blur5}這不是人幹的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:56.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}本大爺可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}只要達到目的 就算失去做人的資格也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:02.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}就算化為惡鬼 本大爺都照做不誤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.03,0:01:04.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}有必要說得這樣誇張嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:06.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}明明只要學會自重一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:07.26,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}自重？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:08.60,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}本大爺沒聽過這個詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:10.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}至少本大爺的字典裡沒這個詞兒...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.86,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:15.40,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}席赫露的胸真大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:18.00,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且形狀也好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:19.86,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可 可愛...？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:20.63,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:23.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我稍微摸一摸也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哈爾希洛 根本不用忍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.30,0:01:29.40,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就摸一下下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你早已敗在自己的本能之下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不然 你早就強行拉著我離開 大喊出聲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:42.93,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就覺得手感肯定會很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太讚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:44.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}這樣啊...我輸了...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我輸了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.13,0:01:49.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:50.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我們啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你這個笨蛋 我們其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.36,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}並沒有輸啊...我們贏了的...！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.43,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再多摸一下下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.26,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}你...說什麼...？？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.76,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要 那樣子摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}這是我們的本能...我們的思想上的勝利...！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:01.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}這怎麼會是我們的失敗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:07.16,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺就像小嬰兒一樣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:02.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}是勝利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}我有說錯什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.20,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好贊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:10.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}原來是我們的勝利嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:12.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}不知不覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}就贏了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}哎...說實在的 好在意啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}雖然並沒有看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.36,0:02:24.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}還沒到頭盔的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1060)\blur5}當然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:30.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡聚集著我們的夢想...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:33.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁著這難得的時機...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:37.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們感受到活著是什麼樣的滋味...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 讓夢的劇場拉開帷幕吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:23.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒這樣子好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:25.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒總這樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.06,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我倒覺得夢兒很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:32.06,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎？才沒有那樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:35.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒哪裡比較可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:38.80,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒不像我這麼胖 看起來還軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:42.46,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 我覺得席赫露不胖的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夢兒的那種柔軟的感覺 看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.23,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誒嘿嘿 好吃的什麼的 夢兒可不是食物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:56.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有點刺激過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完了完了完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這兩個人到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:00.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}腦海中浮現的場景太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(45,45)\fs40\alpha&H82&\3c&H0085FF&\blur5}由於這段沒找到中文翻譯\N而且作者不會日文\N只好對著英語翻譯\N實在對不住啦（渣渣英語）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Want to take a bite? Maybe around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.30,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.56,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Maybe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.73,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.26,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Come on, don't hold back~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}B-but it will hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}（Now, now, over here!）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}I... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:06.50,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能咬這裡一口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.30,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我不能..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.56,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那裡可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:14.73,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但...但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:16.26,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來嘛~不要害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.03,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但..但是那裡會很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.33,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}（來吧 來吧 我來了）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:21.66,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...我不能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.46,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放開我 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.46,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你叫我混蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你難道不想看麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想就這樣放棄麼 這難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:34.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的嚥得下這口氣不後悔麼 哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能會後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能保證絕不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.30,0:05:49.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是繼續這樣下去又怎麼樣 事情又會如何發展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會如何發展
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的我們如此亢奮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繼續這樣下去就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}會陷入無法挽回的境地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:06:00.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我們要回到房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的房間 四個男人的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:08.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:10.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我絕不能忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:28.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我們所有人的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}靈魂的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:35.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無法戀愛的感情 所有的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:39.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部被天空 和天空中的繁星帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:44.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空中的那輪紅月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:50.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一次見到時不可思議的那輪紅月 依舊掛在天空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:55.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}依舊是那麼遙遠 那麼深邃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美麗的夜空中 零落閃爍著的星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}彷彿將要墜落一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:04.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的靈魂在索求著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:11.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}某個遠方無可替代的東西\N這個美妙世界的地平線 一定也在渴求著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家 上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.20,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下雨了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打雷？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.83,TEXT_CN_UP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得找個地方躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:40.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本不可能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索已經有覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}覺悟過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能放手做出這種事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 做不出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:00.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓天都為之顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:04.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:07.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神也在聆聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此 就前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向前衝 沿著這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莫古索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:30.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:38.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們現在真正的感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.66,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍德你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誤 誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼誤會？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你個死色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 露天浴耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}藍德你這個白癡 噁心 色鬼 死變態
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:30.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有多遠滾多遠 永遠不要回來
